Creator - Integrations",description:"A list of integrations for your Solo website.",titleSection:{title:"Integrations",titleDescription:"Extend your Solo website functionality by connecting third-party tools"},cardText:{supportLink:"Learn more"},cards:{calconic:{title:"Calconic",description:"Add an interactive pricing or other calculator to your website. Choose from a prepared template or customize.",link:"https://support.soloist.ai/doc/add-calconic-to-your-solo-website/"},calendly:{title:"Calendly",description:"Let visitors book meetings or schedule appointments on your website with a simple, friendly interface.",link:"https://support.soloist.ai/doc/add-calendly-to-your-solo-website/"},conveyThis:{title:"ConveyThis",description:"Quickly add multi-language support to your website. Translation is automatic, and can be further customized.",link:"https://support.soloist.ai/doc/add-conveythis-to-your-solo-website/"},disqus:{title:"Disqus",description:"Create a more engaging website by adding a space for comments, polls, and more.",link:"https://support.soloist.ai/doc/add-disqus-to-your-solo-website/"},donately:{title:"Donately",description:"Add an interactive component to accept donations on your website to help fund your group or cause.",link:"https://support.soloist.ai/doc/add-donately-to-your-solo-website/"},eventbrite:{title:"Eventbrite",description:"Share event details and purchase options right on your website. Manage registrations on your connected Eventbrite account.",link:"https://support.soloist.ai/doc/add-eventbrite-to-your-solo-website/"},googleCalendar:{title:"Google Calendar",description:"Let website visitors view your schedule directly to help simplify appointment scheduling.",link:"https://support.soloist.ai/doc/add-google-calendar-to-your-solo-website/"},googleForms:{title:"Google Forms",description:"Gather information from visitors directly for contact inquiries, event signups, or feedback.",link:"https://support.soloist.ai/doc/add-google-forms-to-your-solo-website/"},googleTagManager:{title:"Google Tag Manager",description:"Analytics tool to collect visitor actions to help optimize your website experience.",link:"https://support.soloist.ai/doc/how-do-i-view-analytics-for-my-website/"},jotform:{title:"Jotform",description:"Use forms to collect contact info, survey responses, file uploads, and more without writing any code.",link:"https://support.soloist.ai/doc/add-jotform-to-your-solo-website/"},metaPixel:{title:"Meta Pixel",description:"An analytics tool to track conversions and optimize ad performance on Facebook and Instagram.",link:"https://support.soloist.ai/doc/how-do-i-integrate-facebook-pixel/"},openTable:{title:"OpenTable",description:"Leading reservation platform that helps restaurants manage bookings and take reservations directly on their website.",link:"https://support.soloist.ai/doc/add-opentable-to-your-solo-website/"},powr:{title:"POWR",description:"Embed a series of unique and powerful elements, like countdown timers, payment buttons, document requests, and more.",link:"https://support.soloist.ai/doc/add-powr-to-your-solo-website/"},shopify:{title:"Shopify",description:"Display products and allow visitors to make purchases on your website directly.",link:"https://support.soloist.ai/doc/add-a-shopify-collection-to-your-solo-website/"},snapwidget:{title:"SnapWidget",description:"Embed your Facebook, Instagram, or other profile feed on your website.",link:"https://support.soloist.ai/doc/add-a-facebook-feed-to-your-solo-website-with-snapwidget/"},spotify:{title:"Spotify",description:"Embed podcast or playlist content from your connected Spotify account on your website.",link:"https://support.soloist.ai/doc/add-spotify-to-your-solo-website/"},typeform:{title:"Typeform",description:"An online form, survey, and quiz builder that presents questions in a friendly layout.",link:"https://support.soloist.ai/doc/add-typeform-to-your-solo-website/"},weglot:{title:"Weglot",description:"A no-code translation solution that helps you create a multilingual website in just a few steps.",link:"https://support.soloist.ai/doc/add-weglot-to-your-solo-website/"},whatsApp:{title:"WhatsApp",description:"Let visitors start conversations with you instantly from your website using this popular messaging app.",link:"https://support.soloist.ai/doc/how-do-i-add-whatsapp-to-my-website/"},youTube:{title:"YouTube",description:"Embed videos from YouTube into sections formatted to your website layout and theme.",link:"https://support.soloist.ai/doc/can-i-host-videos-or-files/"}}},payments:{success:{title:"Solo - Free AI Website Creator - Payment Success",description:"Your payment was successfully processed.",content:{title:"Payment successful",description:(0,r.jsx)("span",{children:"Thank you for your payment. Your Solo Pro subscription will be processed shortly."}),button:"Return to Solo Website Designer"}},cancelled:{title:"Solo - Free AI Website Creator - Payment Failed",description:"There was an error processing your payment.",content:{title:"Payment failed",description:(0,r.jsx)("span",{children:"There was an error processing your payment. Please try again with a different payment method."}),button:"Open Payments Screen",returnToDesigner:"Return to Solo Website Designer"}}}},sections:[{title:"Header",type:a.WebsiteSectionType.Header,required:!0,default:!0,headerLinkAllowed:!1,maxCount:1},{title:"Introduction",type:a.WebsiteSectionType.Introduction,required:!1,default:!0,headerLinkAllowed:!0,maxCount:3},{title:"Services",type:a.WebsiteSectionType.Services,required:!1,default:!0,headerLinkAllowed:!0,maxCount:3},{title:"Gallery",type:a.WebsiteSectionType.Gallery,required:!1,default:!0,headerLinkAllowed:!0,maxCount:3},{title:"Text Banner",type:a.WebsiteSectionType.QuoteBanner,required:!1,default:!0,headerLinkAllowed:!0,headerLinkSkipDefault:!0,maxCount:3},{title:"Image Banner",type:a.WebsiteSectionType.ImageBanner,required:!1,default:!0,headerLinkAllowed:!1,maxCount:3},{title:"Team",type:a.Web