s-of-service",domainRegistrationAgreement:"https://support.soloist.ai/doc/domain-registration-terms",icannPolicy:"https://www.icann.org/resources/pages/benefits-2013-09-16-en",support:"https://support.soloist.ai",mozillaLabs:"https://newproducts.mozilla.org",releaseNotes:"https://support.soloist.ai/doc/release-notes",googleAnalytics:"https://analytics.google.com",googleAnalyticsGtm:"https://tagmanager.google.com",googleAnalyticsSupport:"https://support.soloist.ai/doc/how-do-i-view-analytics-for-my-website/",schedulingTutorial:"https://support.soloist.ai/doc/how-do-i-create-a-scheduling-link",videoTutorial:"https://support.soloist.ai/doc/can-i-host-videos-or-files/",demoVideo:"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BTBsgSZO-so&t=2s",blog:"https://blog.soloist.ai",reCaptcha:{privacyPolicy:"https://policies.google.com/privacy",termsOfService:"https://policies.google.com/terms"},websiteBuilderGPT:"https://chatgpt.com/g/g-6811592f6ba48191b1d64d7c09624342-solo-ai-website-creator",googleReviews:"https://share.google/FDx57JjYw2sHz1Hez",trustpilotReviews:"https://www.trustpilot.com/review/soloist.ai",indexNow:"https://www.bing.com/indexnow",affiliateLinkProd:"https://affiliates.soloist.ai",affiliateLinkStaging:"https://affiliates.main.soloist.ai",get affiliateLink(){return(0,n.isProd)()?g.externalLinks.affiliateLinkProd:g.externalLinks.affiliateLinkStaging},get referralProgram(){return"".concat(n.baseUrl,"affiliates")},affiliateSignupProd:"https://partners.dub.co/soloai",affiliateSignupStaging:"https://partners.dub.co/soloai-staging",get affiliateSignup(){return(0,n.isProd)()?g.externalLinks.affiliateSignupProd:g.externalLinks.affiliateSignupStaging}},generators:{website:{articleSectionGenerator:{prompt:"For a website named {businessName} based in {businessLocation} engaging in {businessActivities}, create a short article with 2-3 paragraphs with heading for each paragraph. {extraPrompt} This is a summary of my previous website: ***{scrapeSummary}***. The article should showcase the company's expertise, services, and unique selling points. Keep the total length under 5000 characters.",extraPrompt:"The website already has articles titled: {existingArticlesContext}. Please suggest new articles."},contactSectionGenerator:{prompt:"Suggest a compelling title for the contact section of a website for business named {businessName} that engages in {businessActivities}. The title should encourage visitors to contact the business. It should be no more than 4 words."},customerReviewsSectionGenerator:{reviewsPrompt:"I want to build a services business website named {businessName} based in {businessLocation} engaging in {businessActivities}. This is a summary of my previous website: ***{scrapeSummary}*** For my website, please provide or suggest {reviewCount} customer reviews. If the location is not known, please leave it blank.",sampleCustomerReview:"Example Customer Review"},frequentlyAskedQuestionsSection:{prompt:"I want to build a services business website named {businessName} based in {businessLocation} engaging in {businessActivities}. This is a summary of my previous website: ***{scrapeSummary}*** For my website, please provide or suggest {faqCount} fequently asked questions with their respective answers.{extraPrompt}",extraPrompt:"The website already has FAQ questions titled: {existingFaqContext}. Please suggest new questions"},gallerySectionGenerator:{galleryImagePrompt:"I need to query Unsplash for a set of images for the Gallery section of my services business website. The business name is {businessName}. The business description is {businessActivities}. Can you suggest a word or phrase that I can use to search Unsplash for images to serve for the gallery of my website? Please reply with only the word or phrase with no additional text. ".concat(p.prompts.unsplashDisclaimer)},imageBannerSectionGenerator:{imagePrompt:"I need to query Unsplash for a website banner image for my business named {businessName}, specializing in {businessActivities}. Suggest a word or phrase that I should use to search Unsplash. ".concat(p.prompts.unsplashDisclaimer)},introductionSectionGenerator:{prompt:"Suggest an introduction headline for the website {businessName} based in {businessLocation} engaging in {businessActivities}). {extraPrompt} Here’s a summary of my previous website: ***{scrapeSummary}***. Give a headline (≤6 words), a call-to-action button label, a short intro (≤3 sentences), and a word or phrase for Unsplash to find a fitting hero image. ".concat(p.prompts.unsplashDisclaimer),extraPrompt:"This website already has an introduction section with a headline: {existingIntroductionContext}. Please suggest new introduction text."},newsletterSectionGenerator:{prompt:"Suggest a compelling title for the newsletter signup section of a website for a business named {businessName} engaging in {businessActivities}. The title should encourage visitors to stay updated with the business. It should be no more than 4 words."},quoteBannerSectionGenerator:{quotesPrompt:"Suggest an inspirational quote for my business that engages in {activities} based in {businessLocation}. One quote that should not contain more than 12 words. Followed by a smaller call to action quote. Please also include a word or phrase I can use to search Unsplash for an appropriate image to display alongside the inspirational quote. The quotes must be in the language {language}. ".concat(p.prompts.unsplashDisclaimer)},schedulingSectionGenerator:{schedulePrompt:'I want to build a services business website for my business that engages in {businessActivities}. Please suggest a short, compelling heading, and one sentence of contextual body text to encourage them to schedule a time with our business. The customer will have already seen several taglines, so this should focus on the act of connecting. A button will be included, so the text should not include a "click here" or call to action.'},servicesSectionGenerator:{prompt:"For the website {businessName} based in {businessLocation} engaging in {businessActivities}, {extraPrompt}. Here’s a summary of my previous website: ***{scrapeSummary}***. Suggest {servicesToRequest} distinct offerings, each with a title, a brief description (≤2 sentences), and a word or phrase for Unsplash to find a relevant image to display. ".concat(p.prompts.unsplashDisclaimer),extraPrompt:"The website already has services titled: {existingServicesContext}. Please suggest new services"},teamSectionGenerator:{prompt:"I want to build a services business website named {businessName} based in {businessLocation} engaging in {businessActivities}. This is a summary of my previous website: ***{scrapeSummary}*** For my website, please suggest {teamMemberCount} team member bios for persons working at this services business. Each role bio should not be longer than 2 sentences. The bio should reflect the skills required for the types of roles expected at this kind of services business."},videoSectionGenerator:{prompt:"Suggest a title and description for a video that will be displayed on the website of a services business named {businessName} based in {businessLocation} engaging in {businessActivities}. The video title should not be longer than 6 words and the video description should not be longer than 3 sentences."}},businessNameModal:{title:"Business name creator",describeBusiness:"What's your business about?",wordsToInclude:"Words to include",wordsToExclude:"Words to exclude",composing:"Creating...",results:"Results",recompose:"Recreate Names",compose:"Create Names"},businessIdeaModal:{title:"Business idea creator",description:"Let Solo help you brainstorm ideas",composing:"Creating...",results:"Results",recompose:"Recreate Ideas",compose:"Create Ideas"},googleAdCreatorModal:{title:"Google Ad Creator",description:"Create compelling Google Ads for your business with AI assistance. Generate attention-grabbing headlines and persuasive ad copy.",composing:"Creating ad",results:"Your Google Ad",recompose:"Recreate Ad",c