 commission on successful referrals to Solo Pro. Commission rates and terms will be shared when you join the program."},{question:"When do I get paid?",answer:"Payments are processed on a regular schedule once you reach the minimum payout threshold. Details are provided in your affiliate dashboard."},{question:"How do I track my referrals?",answer:"You'll have access to a dedicated affiliate dashboard where you can track clicks, conversions, and earnings in real-time."},{question:"Can I promote Solo on social media?",answer:"Yes! You can share your affiliate links on social media, blogs, websites, and other digital channels. We provide promotional materials to help you get started."},{question:"Is there a minimum payout amount?",answer:"Yes, there is a minimum payout threshold. The specific amount and payment methods will be detailed in your affiliate agreement."},{question:"What if someone doesn't convert right away?",answer:"Your referral link typically has a cookie duration, meaning if someone clicks your link and signs up later within that period, you'll still receive credit."}]},callToAction:{title:"Become a Solo affiliate",description:"Start earning commissions by sharing Solo with your audience.",button:"Join the Affiliate Program",buttonLabel:"Join the Solo Affiliate Program"}},businessNameComposer:{title:"Solo - Free AI Business Name Creator",description:"Use AI to brainstorm possible names for your business",headerText:"Business Name Creator",generatorDescription:"What's your business about?",spinnerText:"Creating Business Names",createButton:"Create Names",recreateButton:"Re-Create Names",subordinateText:"Click on a business name to start building a website",edit:"Edit",results:"Results"},businessIdeaComposer:{title:"Solo - Free AI Business Idea Creator",description:"Use AI to brainstorm possible ideas for your new business",headerText:"Business Idea Creator",generatorDescription:"Let Solo help you brainstorm ideas",spinnerText:"Creating Business Ideas",c